title: [Whistler's Pass, Montane Forest]
description: The trail passes through a small clearing where a dense grove of spruce yields to more thinly-spaced, towering pines.  Whispery starlight pours into the area, bathing onion and catchfly plants with a pale silver glow.

The trail passes through a small clearing where a dense grove of spruce yields to more thinly-spaced, towering pines.  Intense sunlight pours into the area, bathing onion and catchfly plants with a bright golden glow.
